    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    BillingStaffView
    This class provides the billing staff view functionality for interacting with the system.
    CustomerView
    The CustomerView class provides the customer interface for interacting with the store.
    DataLoader
    Component responsible for populating the database with initial sample data.
    Discount
    Represents a discount applied to a specific Merchandise product.
    Discount.DiscountID
    Represents the composite primary key for the Discount entity.
    DiscountRepository
    Repository interface for accessing `Discount` entities from the database.
    DiscountService
    Service class for managing Discount entities.
    DomainObject
    This is an abstract base class for domain objects in the application.
    GlobalView
    The GlobalView class provides global views for the application.
    ManagerView
    The ManagerView class represents the manager's interface for interacting with various views in the application.
    Member
    Represents a member in the system with personal information and membership details.
    MemberRepository
    Repository interface for accessing `Member` entities from the database.
    MemberService
    Service class for managing Member entities.
    MembershipLevel
    Represents the membership levels available in the system.
    Merchandise
    Represents a merchandise item in the store.
    MerchandiseRepository
    Repository interface for accessing Merchandise entities from the database.
    MerchandiseService
    Service class for managing Merchandise entities.
    RegistrationView
    The RegistrationView class represents the view for handling customer registration and membership management.
    Services<T,K>
    A generic service class that provides common CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations for entities that extend DomainObject.
    SignUp
    Represents the signup information of a member at a specific store.
    SignUpRepository
    Repository interface for accessing SignUp entities from the database.
    SignUpService
    Service class responsible for handling operations related to SignUp entities.
    Staff
    Represents a staff member working at a store.
    Staff.Title
    Enum representing the various job titles that a staff member can have.
    StaffRepository
    Repository interface for accessing Staff entities from the database.
    StaffService
    Service class responsible for handling operations related to Staff entities.
    Store
    Represents a store within the application.
    StoreRepository
    Repository interface for accessing Store entities from the database.
    StoreService
    Service class responsible for handling operations related to Store entities.
    Supplier
    Represents a supplier in the system.
    SupplierRepository
    Repository interface for accessing Supplier entities from the database.
    SupplierService
    Service class responsible for handling operations related to Supplier entities.
    Transaction
    Represents a transaction in the system.
    TransactionItem
    Represents an item in a transaction.
    TransactionItemID
    Represents the composite primary key for the `TransactionItem` entity.
    TransactionRepository
    Repository interface for accessing Transaction entities from the database.
    TransactionService
    Service class responsible for handling operations related to Transaction entities.
    WarehouseView
    The WarehouseView class represents the view for managing warehouse operations such as transferring inventory and viewing the entire inventory.
    WolfWRApp
    Main application class for Wolf Wholesale Retail (WolfWR) system.
